<!-- COVER -->
<div class="cover">
  <p class="cover-label">Meridian Health &nbsp;·&nbsp; Brevo CRM</p>
  <h1 class="cover-title" style="page-break-before:avoid">Outstanding Setup Instructions</h1>
  <p class="cover-sub">What needs to be done, by whom, and in what order</p>
  <hr class="gold">
  <div class="cover-meta">
    5 actions &nbsp;·&nbsp; 2 require Netlify access &nbsp;·&nbsp; 3 require Brevo access<br>
    Estimated time: 3–4 hours total (mostly Brevo UI work)<br><br>
    Reference documents in <span style="font-family:monospace">_docs/</span> folder<br>
    Generated May 2026
  </div>
</div>

<!-- TOC -->
<div class="toc-page">
  <h1 class="no-break" style="page-break-before:avoid">Contents &amp; Priority Order</h1>
  <hr class="rule">
  <p style="font-size:10pt;color:#888;margin-bottom:16pt">Complete in sequence. Action 1 is the only hard blocker — nothing flows to Brevo until it is done.</p>
  <div class="toc-row"><span><span class="toc-num">1</span> Add BREVO_API_KEY to Netlify</span><span class="toc-pri">BLOCKER — do first</span></div>
  <div class="toc-row"><span><span class="toc-num">2</span> Set up Brevo contact attributes and tags</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#888">~30 min</span></div>
  <div class="toc-row"><span><span class="toc-num">3</span> Build email templates in Brevo</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#888">~90 min</span></div>
  <div class="toc-row"><span><span class="toc-num">4</span> Build and activate automations in Brevo</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#888">~60 min</span></div>
  <div class="toc-row"><span><span class="toc-num">5</span> Confirm suite number + clinician sign-off</span><span style="font-size:9pt;color:#888">Admin check</span></div>
  <br>
  <div class="note"><strong>Reference documents</strong> (all in the <span class="path">_docs/</span> folder of the project):<br><br>
  <span class="path">brevo-automation-flow.doc</span> — Master spec: all 10 stages, contact attributes, tags, automation descriptions<br>
  <span class="path">brevo-email-copy.html</span> — Verbatim copy for Emails 03–05 and all 15 pathway track emails<br>
  <span class="path">brevo-email-09-post-consultation.html</span> — Email 09 copy and Brevo setup guide<br>
  <span class="path">brevo-stage-08-setup-checklist.html</span> — Step-by-step admin checklist for the 72-hr reminder automation
  </div>
